  - id: ITEM-255
    title: "Implement builtin call capture in replay_conformance.py"
    objective: runtime_replay_capability
    priority: p0
    status: done
    created_at_utc: 2026-03-13T12:42:00Z
    completed_at_utc: 2026-03-13T12:52:00Z
    bucket: runtime
    description: |
      IMPLEMENTED: Builtin call capture instrumentation in replay_conformance.py.
      
      Changes Made:
      - Added eval_expr_with_trace_and_builtin_capture() function that accepts
        a TraceCaptureHook for recording builtin calls
      - Modified _prepare_eval() to wrap all builtin functions with instrumentation
        using _wrap_builtin() helper
      - Updated capture_execution_trace() to use new instrumented evaluation
        and populate builtin_calls from TraceCaptureHook
      - Removed TODO comment indicating builtin call capture was pending
      
      Files Modified:
      - runtime/interpreter_runtime.py (60 lines added, 16 deleted)
        - Added eval_expr_with_trace_and_builtin_capture() function
        - Added _wrap_builtin() helper to wrap builtins with instrumentation
      - runtime/replay_conformance.py (19 lines modified)
        - Updated capture_execution_trace() to use new function
        - builtin_calls now populated from TraceCaptureHook
      
      Validation Results:
      - Builtin call capture verified working: range, len, abs, min, max, is_int, etc.
      - run_public_demo.py --verify-expected: PASSED
      - LND validation: PASSED (4/4)
      - LNC validation: PASSED (1/1)
      - Trace signatures remain deterministic
      - No regression in existing functionality
      
      Product effect: runtime_replay_capability advanced
    acceptance_criteria:
      - TraceCaptureHook records builtin calls during execution - VERIFIED
      - Builtin call records include name, args, result - VERIFIED
      - ExecutionTrace.builtin_calls is populated - VERIFIED
      - run_public_demo.py --verify-expected passes - VERIFIED
      - LND validation passes - VERIFIED
      - LNC validation passes - VERIFIED
    stage: done
    commit: "4133327"

